      "content": "but that sounds so exhausting. just \"being\" when there's nothing there to be. it feels like I'm just maintaining a body that doesn't even belong to me anymore. if the essence of me is gone, then why am i still carrying this heavy, useless thing around? it feels like holding onto something that has no purpose.",
